# Auth Module

User authentication, authorization, and identity management.

## Contents

- `Models/User.php` — The User model (moved from app/Models/)
- `Services/` — Authentication services
- `Contracts/` — Auth service interfaces
- `Events/` — Authentication events (UserRegistered, LoginAttempted, etc.)
- `Routes/` — Auth routes
- `Migrations/` — Auth-related database migrations

## Usage

The User model is available from both:
- `App\Models\User` (alias for backward compatibility)
- `App\Modules\Auth\Models\User` (canonical location)
